For Linux:                                              For windows:

ping google.com   <--------------------------------->   ping google.com
traceroute google.com <----------------------------->   tracert google.com
nslookup google.com <------------------------------->   nslookup google.com
netstat -tulnp <------------------------------------>   netstat -ano
arp -n <-------------------------------------------->   arp -a
rarp -a <------------------------------------------->   (not available by default)
ip addr show/ ip route show <----------------------->   
ifconfig <------------------------------------------>   ipconfig or ipconfig/all
dig google.com <------------------------------------>   nslookup google.com
route -n <------------------------------------------>   route print

